## Deployments

Deployed program will be written to and read from here.

They are JSON files with a UUID as file name.

E.g.:  "4be4dfab-efc8-48b8-a2aa-edcdb0618020.json"

They consist of a `created` timestamp and an R1CS circuit encoded as base64.

For example:
```
{
  "created": 1687847784629,
  "r1cs": ""
}
```
